{"tha-ap93:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap93:0.2":"Sudhavagga ","tha-ap93:0.3":"Sudhapindiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap93:1.1":"“Pujarahe pujayato, ","tha-ap93:1.2":"buddhe yadi va savake; ","tha-ap93:1.3":"Papancasamatikkante, ","tha-ap93:1.4":"tinnasokapariddave. ","tha-ap93:2.1":"Te tadise pujayato, ","tha-ap93:2.2":"nibbute akutobhaye; ","tha-ap93:2.3":"Na sakka punnam sankhatum, ","tha-ap93:2.4":"imettamapi kenaci. ","tha-ap93:3.1":"Catunnamapi dipanam, ","tha-ap93:3.2":"issaram yodha karaye; ","tha-ap93:3.3":"Ekissa pujanayetam, ","tha-ap93:3.4":"kalam nagghati solasim. ","tha-ap93:4.1":"Siddhatthassa naraggassa, ","tha-ap93:4.2":"cetiye phalitantare; ","tha-ap93:4.3":"Sudhapindo maya dinno, ","tha-ap93:4.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap93:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap93:5.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap93:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap93:5.4":"patisankharassidam phalam. ","tha-ap93:6.1":"Ito timsatikappamhi, ","tha-ap93:6.2":"patisankharasavhaya; ","tha-ap93:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap93:6.4":"terasa cakkavattino. ","tha-ap93:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap93:7.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap93:7.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap93:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap93:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sudhapindiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap93:9.1":"Sudhapindiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}